quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  35,45,"N’iyo Allah aza kuba ari uhanira abantu ibyo bakoze, nta kiremwa na kimwe kigenda ku isi yari gusigaho; ariko arabarindiriza kugeza igihe cyagenwe. Kandi igihe cyabo nikigera (nta we uzamucika), kuko mu by’ukuri Allah ari Ubona abagaragu be bihebuje"
  36,1,Yaa-siin
  36,2,Ndahiye iyi Qur’an yuje ubushishozi
  36,3,Mu by’ukuri wowe (Muhamadi) uri umwe mu ntumwa (za Allah)
  36,4,(Kandi uri) mu nzira igororotse (ari yo ya Isilamu)
  36,5,"(Iyi Qur’an) yahishuwe n’Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi (Allah)"
  36,6,"Kugira ngo uburire abantu (ibyo) abakurambere babo batigeze baburirwa, bityo bakaba ari indangare"
  36,7,"Rwose imvugo (y’ibihano) yasohoreye kuri benshi muri bo, ubwo rero ntibazemera"
  36,8,"Mu by’ukuri twashyize iminyururu mu majosi yabo (duhambira amaboko yabo) igeze ku twananwa, ari na yo mpamvu bazaba bararamye"
  36,9,"Kandi twashyize urusika imbere yabo n’inyuma yabo, maze turabapfukirana, bituma batabona"
  36,10,"Wababurira utababurira, kuri bo byose ni kimwe, ntibazemera"
  36,11,Mu by’ukuri (yewe Muhamadi) uwo ushobora kuburira ni ukurikira urwibutso akanatinya (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe atamubona. Muhe inkuru nziza yo kubabarirwa ibyaha no kuzagororerwa ibihembo byiza (Ijuru)
  36,12,"Rwose ni twe tuzura abapfuye, tukanandika ibyo bakoze n’ibyo basize (ibyiza n’ibibi), kandi buri kintu twakibaruye mu gitabo gisobanutse"